The misleading narrative of the canonical faculty productivity trajectory 
Samuel F. Way , Allison C. Morgan , Aaron Clauset , and Daniel B. Larremore 
PNAS October 31, 2017 114 (44) E9216-E9223; first published October 17, 2017 https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.1702121114 
Samuel F. Way 
a Department of Computer Science, University of Colorado , Boulder, CO 80309; 
 
    Find this author on Google Scholar 
    Find this author on PubMed 
    Search for this author on this site 
    For correspondence: daniel.larremore@colorado.edu samuel.way@colorado.edu 
 
