a Department of Computer Science, University of Colorado , Boulder, CO 80309; b BioFrontiers Institute, University of Colorado , Boulder, CO 80303; c Santa Fe Institute , Santa Fe, NM 87501 
 
    Find this author on Google Scholar 
    Find this author on PubMed 
    Search for this author on this site 
    ORCID record for Daniel B. Larremore 
